mesquite.lib

Class NexusBlock

  • java.lang.Object
    • mesquite.lib.NexusBlock
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Identifiable, Listable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CharactersBlock, NexusBlockEditableRaw, TaxaBlock

    public abstract class NexusBlock
extends java.lang.Object
implements Listable, Identifiable
    Represents a block in a NEXUS file. Often contains a reference to the object to be written (e.g., a CharacterData or TreeVector.
